          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: Daniel of Salach, ܡܪܝ ܕܢܐܝܠ ܨ̇ܠܚܝܐ. The first volume of the Commentary of Daniel of Salach, on the Psalms, comprising Pss. i — l.; Daniel of Salach. A letter ofDaniel of SalachtoJohn, abbat of theconvent of Eusebiusatܟܦܪܐ ܕܒܪܬܐ, in the district ofApamea, stating his reasons for writing this commentary, and making it as concise as possible. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 3 items.</note>
            <listRelation type="Wright-BL-Taxonomy">
              <relation name="dcterms:type" ref="http://purl.org/dc/terms/type" active="https://bl.syriac.uk/ms/841" passive="#theo-single">
